OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable cloud, and some sunny
OL,6,Fspells through the morning. Showers
OL,7,Fdeveloping across northwestern parts
OL,8,Fby mid-afternoon, before spreading
OL,9,Fsoutheast later. These occasionally
OL,10,Fheavy with a very isolated rumble of
OL,11,Fthunder possible. Light winds, and
OL,12,Ffeeling warm in any sunny spells.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers fading through the
OL,15,Fevening, with some brief clear spells
OL,16,Flikely. Low cloud, mist and the odd
OL,17,Fspot of drizzle then spreading inland
OL,18,Fafter midnight. Less cold than recent
OL,19,Fnights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
